Account Information' and select 'Delete Account'. Please note that activity generated prior to deletion will remain stored by us and information submitted publicly may remain publicly accessible. If you need our help deleting your Account, please <span style="color: rgb(70, 100, 134); font-weight: bold;">reach us through email</span>.</span></p><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-00e681af"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3f8800e6">6. What happens when there are changes to this Privacy Policy?<br></span></p><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-8db0c9de"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-4c738db0">We may modify or update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect the changes in our business and practices. When we change this Privacy Policy in a material manner we will let you know and update the 'last modified' date at the top of this page. We may provide notice of changes to this Privacy Policy through a pop-up or banner within the Service, by sending an email to any address you may have used to register for an account, or through other mechanisms. Continuing to use our Service after we provide you notice of changes to this Privacy Policy means that you are consenting to the changes.<br><br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-7ad20c0f" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-d44eafc7 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-0b82d44e" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-47f56012"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a49f47f5">Help is just an email away</span></h3><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f1677ad2"><span dat